                        <div id="page-title">
                            中国分部异常项目
                        </div>
                    

                    

                    



                    <div id="page-content">
                        

<p><strong>前言：</strong>SCP基金会中国分部发现了为数不少的项目无用而不值得进一步关注。本文件列出了那些激起了一些好奇心的项目。如果这些项目的知识在将来变得有用或必要，则可以将其作为一种资源。<br />
— █████博士，Site-CN-██研究主管</p>
<p>欲查看已归档的异常项目记录，请<a href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn-arc">点击这里</a>。</p>
<hr />
<div class="list-pages-box">    <div class="list-pages-item">


<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button create-button" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00522/parentPage/log-of-anomalous-items-cn/#_editpage">添加新的记录</a></p>
</div>
    
    
    
    </div>
<p style="text-align: center;">显示顺序：<a href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn/order/rating%20desc">评分较高</a> | <a href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn/order/rating">评分较低</a> | <a href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn/order/name">最早发布</a> | <a href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn/order/name%20desc">最新发布</a> | <a href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn/order/random">随机</a></p>
<p><strong>提示：</strong>如果你希望改变你的评分，请先点击“X”取消你的评分，再重新评分。</p>
<hr />
<div class="list-pages-box">    <div class="list-pages-item">


<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00471/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>项目描述：</strong>一把普通的乌木椅子，但除了方琪博士外的如何基金会员工都会认为项目具有重大研究价值，并尝试将其归为SCP项目。<br />
<strong>回收日期：</strong>20██/██/██<br />
<strong>回收地点：</strong>方琪博士的个人实验室<br />
<strong>当前状态：</strong>被方琪博士牢牢地嵌在了其实验室的水泥地上<br />
<strong>笔记：</strong>方琪博士：那只是我姐留下的一把普通的乌木椅子啊，我只是喜欢ta才带到基金会的呀！<br />
Dr.Give Up:我知道了！你才是SCP-2066██本体吧！而那椅子就是SCP-2066██-1！<br />
方琪博士：啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！！！！！</p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00471" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00471" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00471-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/i-give-up" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6937520); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6937520&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610222219" alt="I give up" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6937520)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/i-give-up" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6937520); return false;">I give up</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1606644660 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">29 Nov 2020 10:11</span></p>
</div>
<hr />
</div>
<div class="list-pages-item">


<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00435/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>项目描述：</strong>一个蓝色四指环型握力器，其上用白色油漆印有“劣质产品® ”字样，当有人员把四根手指都伸入指环时，指环的半径将缩小10~26%，该异常影响通常持续时间从5分钟到█小时不等，期间该物品无法被以任何方式破坏<br />
<strong>回收日期：</strong>2020/10/5<br />
<strong>回收地点：</strong>Site-CN-82训练区域健身区C2号器材架<br />
<strong>当前状态：</strong>于Site-CN-82异常物品仓库中<br />
<strong>笔记：</strong><em>“喂喂喂你这样是拔不出来的！”——Dr.Gaster，选自事故记录-H0714</em><br />
<em>“哼！啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！”Dr.Cerberus，选自事故记录-H0714</em></p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00435" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00435" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00435-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gaster-master" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3398699); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3398699&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610222219" alt="Gaster Master" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3398699)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gaster-master" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3398699); return false;">Gaster Master</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1602080060 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">07 Oct 2020 14:14</span></p>
</div>
<hr />
</div>
<div class="list-pages-item">


<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00476/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>项目描述：</strong><span style="text-decoration: line-through;">52</span>50片███牌止咳药，服用后会使服用对象的声音向异性的声线变化。<br />
<strong>回收日期：</strong>20██/██/██<br />
<strong>回收地点：</strong>Site-CN-07医务室药柜上<br />
<strong>当前状态：</strong>存放于Site-CN-07的低价值异常物品储藏室内。<br />
<strong>笔记：</strong><em>我就吃了两片止咳药啊！为什么有这么多男的来对我表白啊啊啊！！！——研究员lush</em><br />
<em>可能是因为你的体型就挺像女性，还是长发，现在声音也变了&#8230;..——██博士</em></p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00476" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00476" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00476-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lush-favor" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6981514); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6981514&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610222219" alt="Lush_Favor" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6981514)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lush-favor" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6981514); return false;">Lush_Favor</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1607183218 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">05 Dec 2020 15:46</span></p>
</div>
<hr />
</div>
<div class="list-pages-item">


<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00520/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>项目描述：</strong>一根长约1.3米的木制棍子，任何人员持有时都会产生用其防身的冲动。<br />
<strong>回收日期：</strong>20██/██/██<br />
<strong>回收地点：</strong>Site-CN-09站点前门草坪中<br />
<strong>当前状态：</strong>保存于11号低风险物品储藏间<br />
<strong>笔记：</strong>世间竟有如此宝刀？——捡到该项目的pablo<br />
你幼不幼稚?——看到pablo挥舞该项目的Lamp</p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00520" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00520" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00520-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/crow-pablo" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6518998); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6518998&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610222220" alt="Crow pablo" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6518998)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/crow-pablo" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6518998); return false;">Crow pablo</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1610184482 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">09 Jan 2021 09:28</span></p>
</div>
<hr />
</div>
<div class="list-pages-item">


<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00214/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>项目描述：</strong>一把手枪样式的口腔清新剂，对无生命物体扣动扳机，枪口会射出一颗完整的.45子弹，但如果对人类口腔扣动扳机，枪口会射出1立方厘米的口腔清新剂。<br />
<strong>回收日期：</strong>20██/██/██<br />
<strong>回收地点：</strong>[已编辑]<br />
<strong>当前状态：</strong>保存在Dr.bert的私人物品里<br />
<strong>笔记：</strong>王特工：“哦天啊。一个人居然将手枪放在自己嘴巴里！！！”<br />
Dr.bert：“emm&#8230;”</p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00214" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00214" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00214-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/crimaster" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6106971); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6106971&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610222220" alt="Crimaster" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6106971)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/crimaster" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6106971); return false;">Crimaster</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1589973470 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">20 May 2020 11:17</span></p>
</div>
<hr />
</div>
<div class="list-pages-item">


<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00419/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong><span style="font-size:x-large;">项目描述</span>：</strong>一副由<span style="font-size:x-large;">████公司</span>生产的<span style="font-size:x-large;">███眼镜</span>，会使<span style="font-size:x-large;">佩戴者</span>认为其所看到的<span style="font-size:x-large;">文字</span>中的<span style="font-size:x-large;">名词部分</span>比<span style="font-size:x-large;">其他部分</span>要大一些。<br />
<strong>回收<span style="font-size:x-large;">日期</span>：</strong>20██/██/██<br />
<strong>回收<span style="font-size:x-large;">地点</span>：</strong><span style="font-size:x-large;">████公司专卖店</span>。<br />
<strong>当前<span style="font-size:x-large;">状态</span>：</strong>存放于Dr.K的<span style="font-size:x-large;">办公室</span>内。<br />
<strong><span style="font-size:x-large;">笔记</span>：</strong><em>确实是大<strong>亿</strong>些。&#8212;Dr.K</em></p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00419" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00419" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
