<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00269/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>项目描述：</strong>一面挂镜，当一名正常人类个体面对该镜子5秒以上时，此人在镜子中的映像突然消失<br />
<strong>回收日期：</strong>20██/██/██<br />
<strong>回收地点：</strong>Site64的一间公共厕所中<br />
<strong>当前状态：</strong>保存于Site64异常物品仓库<br />
<strong>笔记：</strong><br />
“大晚上的路过镜子看不见人可真是恐怖”——初级研究员Ginger</p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00269" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00269" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00269-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ginger249-jackie" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4136896); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4136896&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610222220" alt="Ginger249-Jackie" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4136896)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ginger249-jackie" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4136896); return false;">Ginger249-Jackie</a></span></p>
